conjunction with a proposed expansion by Kern River Gas Transmission Company (``Kern River'') of 452 Mmcf/d. Kern
River's proposal is currently pending at Docket No. CP92-198-000.

Mojave states that the Amendment has two purposes. One is to identify 29 minor route modifications to the previously-proposed
