No changes to the limiting conditions for operation for containment 
integrity are proposed as part of this amendment request. The 
proposed change does not involve any physical changes to the plant or 
any changes to plant operations. Thus, the proposed change does not 
create the possibility of a new or different kind of accident from any 
accident previously evaluated. 



