a gradual change in core flow. Thus, the response to a startup 
of an idle recirculation pump remains bounded by the transient 
analysis and safety margins will be maintained in the transient 
analyses. 
Changes to the fire protection equipment will still maintain the 
capability to shutdown the plant in the event of a fire. 




